    "description": {
      "zh": "Steyr AUG A1是一款使用5.56x45弹药的无托式突击步枪，由奥地利Steyr-Daimler-Puch公司生产。AUG因其良好的人体工学设计、高精度、低后坐力以及高可靠性而著称。这款步枪的未来化设计也独树一帜。",
      "en": "Steyr AUG A1 is a 5.56x45 bullpup assault rifle, developed by the Austrian company Steyr-Daimler-Puch. AUG is known for good ergonomics, decent accuracy, low recoil and sufficient reliability. The rifle also stands out for its futuristic design."
    },
